The Centre for Destitute Empowerment International (CDEI), a Lagos-based charity organisation, has announced the transition of its Founder/President, Pastor Samson Okoliko. A statement from the centre said funeral arrangements would begin with a service of songs at his home, 8, Makanjuola Close, Paiko, Idimu, in Lagos, on Monday, while interment takes place on February 19 at Kwali, in Abuja. He is survived by a wife and children.